videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk takes the ball coast to coast and hits the game-winning shot for Kansas before time expires in a 90-88 victory over Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Mykhailiuk wins it for Kansas with buzzer-beating shot) 2017/1/3

videos.headline: Mykhailiuk wins it for Kansas with buzzer-beating shot

videos.description: Bruce Weber alludes that the refs missed a travel call on Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk's game-winning shot, but assigns most of the blame to his team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Weber on no-call on final play: 'Everybody knows what happened') 2017/01/03

videos.headline: Weber on no-call on final play: 'Everybody knows what happened'
